Minimum system requirements

# OS: Windows® Vista / XP / 7
# Processor:Intel® Core™2 Duo E6600 or AMD Phenom™ X3 8750 or better

# Video: Shader 3.0 or better 256MB NVIDIA® GeForce® 8600GT / ATI Radeon® X1950Pro or better
